クラス ThrowingPrintWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.Writer
      • org.eclipse.jgit.util.io.ThrowingPrintWriter
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable

    public class ThrowingPrintWriter
extends Writer
    An alternative PrintWriter that doesn't catch exceptions.
